			"id":"v86nu669mq9l7",
			"name":"等价的Python代码：\n```python\ndef quick_sort(arr: list):\n    stack = []\n    stack.append((0, len(arr) - 1))\n    while len(stack) != 0:\n        low, high = stack.pop()\n        if low >= high:\n            continue\n        pivot = arr[high]\n        i = low - 1\n        for j in range(low, high):\n            if arr[j] <= pivot:\n                i += 1\n                arr[i], arr[j] = arr[j], arr[i]\n        arr[i + 1], arr[high] = arr[high], arr[i + 1]\n        stack.append((low, i))\n        stack.append((i + 2, high))\n    return arr\n```",
			"parent":"",
